Package: testIsLoadedUpstream
Title: Helper for the isNamespaceLoaded() Regression Test (Upstream)
Version: 1.0
Author: R Core
Maintainer: R Core <R-core@almost.r-project.org>
Description: Used by reg-packages.R to exercise isNamespaceLoaded() during
 cyclic namespace loading.  Its .onLoad reaches into testIsLoadedDownstream,
 which is why that package is only a soft (Suggests) dependency.
Suggests: testIsLoadedDownstream
